#: inc/comp/migration/DashboardTileMigrationMajor2.php:84
msgid "Transparency & Consent Framework (TCF)"
msgstr "Marco de transparencia y consentimiento (TCF)"

#: inc/comp/migration/DashboardTileMigrationMajor2.php:85
msgid ""
"You can now obtain consent according to the TCF standard from IAB Europe. "
"You need this type of consent mostly when you work with big marketers, e.g. "
"Google Adsense, so they can be sure that you have obtained consent from your "
"visitors. If you turn on TCF compatibility, some features of Real Cookie "
"Banner will change so that your cookie banner is compliant with the rules of "
"the standard."
msgstr ""
"Ahora puede obtener el consentimiento según el estándar TCF de IAB Europe. "
"Usted necesita este tipo de consentimiento sobre todo cuando trabaja con "
"grandes empresas de marketing, por ejemplo Google Adsense, para que puedan "
"estar seguros de que usted ha obtenido el consentimiento de sus visitantes. "
"Si activa la compatibilidad TCF, algunas funciones de Real Cookie Banner "
"cambiarán para que su banner de cookies cumpla con las reglas del estándar."

#: inc/comp/migration/DashboardTileMigrationMajor2.php:91
#: inc/comp/migration/DashboardTileMigrationMajor2.php:109
msgid "Already enabled"
msgstr "Ya está habilitado"

#: inc/comp/migration/DashboardTileMigrationMajor2.php:92
