#: inc/comp/migration/DashboardTileMigrationMajor4.php:217
msgid ""
"https://devowl.io/knowledge-base/cookie-banner-swiss-data-protection-fadp/"
msgstr ""
"https://devowl.io/knowledge-base/cookie-banner-swiss-data-protection-fadp/"

#: inc/comp/migration/DashboardTileMigrationMajor4.php:222
