#: inc/view/Notices.php:583
#, php-format
msgid ""
"There seems to be something generally wrong with the REST API of your "
"WordPress instance. Please deactivate Real Cookie Banner and then check "
"under <a href=\"%s\">Tools > Site Health</a> whether errors regarding the "
"REST API are listed there."
msgstr ""
"Parece que hay algún error general en la API REST de su instancia de "
"WordPress. Por favor, desactive Real Cookie Banner y después compruebe en <a "
"href=\"%s\">Tools > Site Health</a> si allí aparecen errores relativos a la "
"API REST."

#: inc/view/Notices.php:616
msgid ""
"<strong>Consent cannot be saved in the cookie banner:</strong> Website "
"visitors (not logged into WordPress) currently cannot save consents in the "
"cookie banner. This may result in the cookie banner being displayed again "
"each time the website visitor visits a page."
msgstr ""
"<strong>El consentimiento no puede guardarse en el banner de cookies:</"
"strong> Actualmente, los visitantes del sitio web (que no hayan iniciado "
"sesión en WordPress) no pueden guardar los consentimientos en el banner de "
"cookies. Esto puede provocar que el banner de cookies vuelva a mostrarse "
"cada vez que el visitante del sitio web visite una página."

#. translators:
#: inc/view/Notices.php:629
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The consent would be saved via the WP REST API route %s. The following "
"problems with your WordPress installation were detected during the automatic "
"error analysis:"
msgstr ""
"El consentimiento se guardaría a través de la ruta WP REST API %s. Durante "
"el análisis automático de errores se detectaron los siguientes problemas en "
"su instalación de WordPress:"

#. translators:
#: inc/view/Notices.php:653
#, php-format
msgid ""
"HTTP error code <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/"
"Status/%1$d\" target=\"_blank\"><code>%1$d</code></a> has been returned by "
"the server. This indicates that the <a href=\"%2$s\" target=\"_blank\">WP "
"REST API may have been proactively blocked</a>."
msgstr ""
"Código de error HTTP <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/"
"HTTP/Status/%1$d\" target=\"_blank\"><code>%1$d</code> </a> ha sido devuelto "
"por el servidor. Esto indica que la API REST de WP <a href=\"%2$s\" "
"target=\"_blank\">puede haber sido bloqueada proactivamente</a>."

#: inc/view/Notices.php:658
msgid ""
"https://devowl.io/knowledge-base/wordpress-rest-api-does-not-respond/#how-"
"can-i-enable-the-wordpress-rest-api-in-my-website"
msgstr ""
"https://devowl.io/knowledge-base/wordpress-rest-api-does-not-respond/#how-"
"can-i-enable-the-wordpress-rest-api-in-my-website"

#. translators:
#: inc/view/Notices.php:666
msgid ""
"Response from the server is malformed. This indicates, for example, that "
"another plugin is manipulating the response. In the following, you find the "
"server response:"
msgstr ""
"La respuesta del servidor está malformada. Esto indica, por ejemplo, que "
"otro plugin está manipulando la respuesta. A continuación se muestra la "
"respuesta del servidor:"

#. translators:
#: inc/view/Notices.php:675
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Cookie with the saved consent (name starts with <code>real_cookie_banner</"
"code>) was not part of the server response. Perhaps you have configured your "
"<a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank\">webserver to drop all cookies before "
"sending the response</a>."
msgstr ""
"La cookie con el consentimiento guardado (el nombre empieza por "
"<code>real_cookie_banner</code>) no formaba parte de la respuesta del "
"servidor. Tal vez haya configurado su servidor web <a href=\"%s\" "
"target=\"_blank\">para que elimine todas las cookies antes de enviar la "
"respuesta</a>."

#: inc/view/Notices.php:679
msgid ""
"https://devowl.io/knowledge-base/cookie-banner-displayed-every-subpage/"
"#cause-4-server-discards-all-cookies"
msgstr ""
"https://devowl.io/knowledge-base/cookie-banner-displayed-every-subpage/"
"#cause-4-server-discards-all-cookies"

#. translators:
#: inc/view/Notices.php:687
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Cookie <code>%1$s</code> with saved consent has been responded by server, "
"but with the invalid cookie path <code>%2$s</code>. You may have an <a "
"href=\"%3$s\" target=\"_blank\">error in your WordPress configuration file</"
"a>."
msgstr ""
"Cookie <code>%1$s</code> con consentimiento guardado ha sido respondida por "
"el servidor, pero con la ruta de cookie inválida <code>%2$s</code> . Es "
"posible que tenga un error <a href=\"%3$s\" target=\"_blank\">en su archivo "
"de configuración de WordPress</a>."

#: inc/view/Notices.php:693
msgid ""
"https://devowl.io/knowledge-base/cookie-banner-displayed-every-subpage/"
"#cause-2-incorrect-cookie-path"
msgstr ""
"https://devowl.io/knowledge-base/cookie-banner-displayed-every-subpage/"
"#cause-2-incorrect-cookie-path"

#. translators:
#: inc/view/Notices.php:701
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Cookie <code>%1$s</code> with saved consent has been responded to by the "
"server, but with a <code>HttpOnly</code> flag, which means that the Real "
"Cookie Banner JavaScript does not have permission to read it. You probably "
"have <a href=\"%2$s\" target=\"_blank\">too strict security settings "
"configured in your web server</a>."
msgstr ""
"Cookie <code>%1$s</code> con consentimiento guardado ha sido respondida por "
"el servidor, pero con una bandera <code>HttpOnly</code>, lo que significa "
"que el Real Cookie Banner JavaScript no tiene permiso para leerla. "
"Probablemente tenga <a href=\"%2$s\" target=\"_blank\">configurados unos "
"parámetros de seguridad demasiado estrictos en su servidor web</a>."

#: inc/view/Notices.php:706
msgid ""
"https://devowl.io/knowledge-base/cookie-banner-displayed-every-subpage/"
"#cause-3-cookie-not-accessible-via-javascript"
msgstr ""
"https://devowl.io/knowledge-base/cookie-banner-displayed-every-subpage/"
"#cause-3-cookie-not-accessible-via-javascript"

#. translators:
#: inc/view/Notices.php:714
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Response of the server contains a <code>Location</code> header, which leads "
"to a redirection of the save request instead of saving. You probably have an "
"<a href=\"%2$s\" target=\"_blank\">incorrect trailing slash configuration in "
"your web server</a>."
msgstr ""
"La respuesta del servidor contiene una cabecera <code>Ubicación</code>, lo "
"que provoca una redirección de la solicitud de guardado en lugar de "
"guardado. Probablemente tenga una <a href=\"%2$s\" "
"target=\"_blank\">configuración incorrecta de la barra diagonal final en su "
"servidor web</a>."

#: inc/view/Notices.php:719
msgid ""
"https://devowl.io/knowledge-base/wordpress-rest-api-does-not-respond/#i-can-"
"read-data-but-not-write"
msgstr ""
"https://devowl.io/knowledge-base/wordpress-rest-api-does-not-respond/#i-can-"
"read-data-but-not-write"

#. translators:
#: inc/view/Notices.php:727
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Since the request returned a <code>403</code> error, it is possible that the "
"IP of your server has been blocked for internal loopback requests. We have "
"checked the <code>.htaccess</code> file and found that the following line "
"could be the trigger for this, which you should check and remove: <code>%s</"
"code>."
msgstr ""
"Dado que la petición devolvía un error <code>403</code>, es posible que la "
"IP de su servidor haya sido bloqueada para peticiones loopback internas. "
"Hemos comprobado el archivo <code>.htaccess</code> y hemos encontrado que la "
"siguiente línea podría ser el desencadenante de esto, que debería comprobar "
"y eliminar: <code>%s</code> ."

#. translators:
#: inc/view/Notices.php:748
#, php-format
msgid ""
"We have <a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank\">explained typical misconfigurations "
"and solutions</a> for this issue in a detailed article. If you do not know "
"how to solve this problem, please contact the technical contact person for "
"your website!"
msgstr ""
"Hemos <a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank\">explicado los errores de "
"configuración típicos y las soluciones</a> para este problema en un artículo "
"detallado. Si no sabe cómo resolver este problema, póngase en contacto con "
"la persona de contacto técnico de su sitio web!"

#: inc/view/Notices.php:753
msgid "https://devowl.io/knowledge-base/cookie-banner-displayed-every-subpage/"
msgstr ""
"https://devowl.io/knowledge-base/cookie-banner-displayed-every-subpage/"

#: inc/view/Notices.php:774
msgid "Check consent storage process again"
msgstr "Vuelva a comprobar el proceso de almacenamiento del consentimiento"

